title: Team Insurgency Looking for top Laner + Support
body:
Team Insurgency looking for a top laner and support for OOL and future endeavours

We have in the two tournaments we have competed in made it to knock outs both times. A solid Top laner would give us a significant edge in competitive.
We are also looking for a new support to round out the roster, upon successful application the applicant will take over our current supports role.

Please use the website application to apply for either position and I will get back to you as soon as possible.

Average Ranking of our team is around Diamond

Thank you
